## License Conditions

1. **Scope**: This addendum applies to all personal or non-commercial use of the Licensed Work.

2. **Contribution Requirement**: You may use the Licensed Work only if you make a meaningful Contribution to the original repository. This Contribution may be submitted before or shortly after use begins.

3. **Commercial Use Prohibited**: This variant of the RCL does not permit commercial use under any circumstance.

4. **Acknowledgment Requirement**: Any redistribution (even personal) must include the following notice:

   > "This product includes or uses the \[Licensed Work] and has contributed to its development."

5. **Enforcement**: Use of the Licensed Work without satisfying the Contribution requirement is a breach of this license addendum and may terminate all granted rights.

6. **Disclaimer**: This addendum is provided "AS IS" without warranty of any kind.

